This paper is about automated machine learning, which is a subfield of machine learning. The paper specifically focuses on multi-objective optimization and constraints in machine learning problems. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). The paper also discusses distributed computing, which could fall under cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing). Finally, the paper presents real-world case studies, which could fall under cs.SE (Software Engineering).
